+ *	Copyright  Aaron Hopkins <tools [at] die net>, 2002
+ *
+ *	Based on ipt_REJECT.c and offering functionality similar to
+ *	LaBrea <http://www.hackbusters.net/LaBrea/>.
+ *
+ *	<<<
